{"tid":412564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係又鍾意J-POP，又仲意K-POP？","createTime":"2017-09-24T18:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T18:15:14.000Z","uid":139462,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fcbd0225af1f872cd763c164dad53d084b38564","tid":412564,"uid":139462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"都幾慘。。。。。。。<br />\n響網絡上面，同時之間又會俾人鬧毒L、宅男，又會俾人鬧韓狗、偽泡菜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有乜值得好拗姐？<br />\n唔同人都會有自己嘅喜好，不論係J-POP 又好K-POP 又好都有唔同嘅優點架啦<br />\n根本冇必要響到拗，更加冇必要互相攻擊<br />\n自己聽番自己鍾意嘅音樂就得啦<br />\n係唔係？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（純粹想呻下）<br />\n（冇挑起紛爭之心）<br />\n（雖然都知應該會有負皮，留言攻擊，但都想講下）"}]}